{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1673-06_078", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Elegie sur une joüissance, en songe]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", 1673 (tome VI), p. 78-88."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vociy quelques Vers qui vous divertiront peut-estre davantage."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Elegie."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center b"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "JE vous aime, Amarante, & l’ardeur qui me presse"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Depuis assez long-temps vous fait voir ma tendresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mon cœur à vos pieds avec mille plaisirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous a sacrifié ses plus ardens soûpirs ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Toûjours constant, toûjours & discret & fidelle,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Avec les mesmes feux, avec le mesme zele."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Il a bruslé malgré vos infidelitez,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Il a mesme adoré jusqu’à vos cruautez :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "De sa tendresse, enfin, pleinement convaincuë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Le voyant si constant, vous estes revenuë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Et le votre charmé d’un si fidelle amour,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "A sçeu flater le mien d’un aimable retour."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Hé bien nous nous aimons, mon cœur est tout au vostre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Nos Lettres, nos soûpirs nous l’ont dit l’un à l’autre ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais à quoy serviront nos Lettres, nos soûpirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Si nous n’avons tous deux d’autres pressans desirs ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Que nous servira d’estre en la fleur de nostre age,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "D’avoir de la tendresse, & n’en point faire usage ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Et de ne point gouster les plaisirs innocens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[20]/text()[1]", "text": "Dont un parfaict amour a charmé tous nos sens ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[21]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[21]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! quand je vous voy, toute mon ame émeuë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[22]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[22]/text()[1]", "text": "Se trouble & s’interdit à cette chere veuë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[23]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[23]/text()[1]", "text": "Mille brûlans desirs assassinent mon cœur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[24]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[24]/text()[1]", "text": "Il se coule en mes sens une aimable langueur,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[25]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[25]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne sçay quoy de doux me saisit & me presse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[26]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[26]/text()[1]", "text": "Mon cœur ne peut suffire à toute sa tendresse,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[27]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[27]/text()[1]", "text": "Nuit & jour il soûpire, & mesme loin de vous"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[28]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[28]/text()[1]", "text": "Mon esprit n’est remply que d’un objet si doux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[29]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[29]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous occupez toûjours mon cœur & ma pensée."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[30]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[30]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! il m’en souvient ; pendant la nuit passée"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[31]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[31]/text()[1]", "text": "Je revois que j’estois tout seul à vos genoux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[32]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[32]/text()[1]", "text": "N’ayant que nostre amour pour témoin avec nous."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[33]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[33]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans les premiers instans de nos langues muettes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[34]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[34]/text()[1]", "text": "Nos yeux & nos soûpirs furent les interpretes,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[35]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[35]/text()[1]", "text": "Mon amour plus hardy s’expliqua la premier,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[36]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[36]/text()[1]", "text": "Le vostre plus timide éclata le dernier."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[37]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[37]/text()[1]", "text": "Cent promesses alors, tendres & mutuelles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[38]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[38]/text()[1]", "text": "Mille & mille sermens de nous estre fidelles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[39]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[39]/text()[1]", "text": "Mes larmes, mes soûpirs & mes empressements"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[40]/text()[1]", "text": "Sembloient vous ébranler dans ces heureux momens ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[41]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[41]/text()[1]", "text": "Vostre cœur me parut s’atendrir à ma veuë,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[42]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[42]/text()[1]", "text": "Et mon émotion rendit votre ame émeuë ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[43]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[43]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous pressay, vos mains repoussoient foiblement"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[44]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[44]/text()[1]", "text": "L’impetueux transport d’un si beau mouvement."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[45]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[45]/text()[1]", "text": "La langueur de vos yeux qui sembloit les dédire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[46]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[46]/text()[1]", "text": "Me disoit en secret, voy mon cœur qui soûpire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[47]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[47]/text()[1]", "text": "Je l’entendois ; le mien si tendre & si discret,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[48]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[48]/text()[1]", "text": "Par ses brûlant transport vous pressoit en secret."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[49]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[49]/text()[1]", "text": "Voyant des yeux si doux, une bouche adorable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[50]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[50]/text()[1]", "text": "J’estois dans un estat & tendre & pitoyable,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[51]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[51]/text()[1]", "text": "Une gorge charmante allumant mes desirs,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[52]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[52]/text()[1]", "text": "S’enfloit & repoussoit mes mains par vos soûpirs :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[53]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[53]/text()[1]", "text": "Enfin je m’enhardis, sur vostre aimable bouche"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[54]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[54]/text()[1]", "text": "Un long baiser la sçeut rendre un peu moins farouche,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[55]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[55]/text()[1]", "text": "J’en appuye un second si charmant & si doux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[56]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[56]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’enyvrè de plaisirs & mourant pres de vous,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[57]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[57]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur nos levres alors nos deux ames unies,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[58]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[58]/text()[1]", "text": "Goustoient en se pasmant des douceurs infinies."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[59]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[59]/text()[1]", "text": "Je fis plus, & prenant de plus hardis desseins,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[60]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[60]/text()[1]", "text": "Je les exectutay par mes tremblantes mains."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[61]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[61]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah ! que j’eus de plaisirs, que de charmantes choses"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[62]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[62]/text()[1]", "text": "S’offrirent à mes yeux, que de Lys & de Roses"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[63]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[63]/text()[1]", "text": "Je pillay, je foulay dans mes plus beaux transports,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[64]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[64]/text()[1]", "text": "Ebloüy des beautez d’un adorable corps :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[65]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[65]/text()[1]", "text": "Transformé tout en vous ; & hors tout de moy-mesme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[66]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[66]/text()[1]", "text": "Je tombe & je me pasme en ce desordre extréme,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[67]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[67]/text()[1]", "text": "Je m’agite, me tourne & dans ces doux efforts,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[68]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[68]/text()[1]", "text": "En croyant embrasser encor un si beau corps,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[69]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[69]/text()[1]", "text": "Je m’esveille, me trouve en mon lit triste & sombre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[70]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[70]/text()[1]", "text": "Et vis évanoüir mesme jusqu’à vostre ombre."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[71]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[71]/text()[1]", "text": "Voilà de mon sommeil le succez & le fruit :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[72]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[72]/text()[1]", "text": "Que j’aurois immolé de jours pour cette nuit !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[73]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[73]/text()[1]", "text": "Nuit qui me fut si chere, & dont le doux mensonge"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[74]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[74]/text()[1]", "text": "M’a tant fait en veillant souhaiter ce beau songe ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[75]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[75]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais si ce songe enfin devenoit veritè,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[76]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[76]/text()[1]", "text": "Pourions-nous pas en faire une realitè ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[77]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[77]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous aime, ou plutost mon ame vous adore,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[78]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[78]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous m’aimez & brûlez du feu qui me devore ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[79]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[79]/text()[1]", "text": "Je suis respectueux, ardent, tendre & discret,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[80]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[80]/text()[1]", "text": "Je sçais si bien me taire & garder le secret ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[81]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[81]/text()[1]", "text": "Parlez, à quoy tient-il, ma divine Amarante,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[82]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[82]/text()[1]", "text": "Et que vous servira d’estre belle & charmante,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[83]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[83]/text()[1]", "text": "Moy fidelle, soûmis, discret, tendre, amoureux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[84]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[84]/text()[1]", "text": "Si nous laissons languir le plus beau de nos feux ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[85]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[85]/text()[1]", "text": "Si pour moy vostre cœur & languissant & tendre….."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[86]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[86]/text()[1]", "text": "Est-il assez cruel encor pour se defendre ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[87]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[87]/text()[1]", "text": "Ayant donnè le cœur, que peut-on refuser ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[88]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[88]/text()[1]", "text": "Ah ! si je vous croyois, il pouroit tout oser ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[89]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[89]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais si le mien a fait cette illustre conqueste,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[90]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[90]/text()[1]", "text": "Que de charmans plaisirs dans un doux teste-à-teste !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[91]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[91]/text()[1]", "text": "Oüy, c’est là qu’il m’en faut expliquer avec vous :"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[92]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[92]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous m’aimez, je vous aime, helas ! qu’attendons-nous ?"}]}], "attributes": {"rend": "border"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces Vers ont plû à beaucoup de Gens, & je croy que les Amans passionnez les doivent trouver à leur goust."}]}]}